# BettingTools Platform - Project Information

This project is a betting analytics and tipster platform that allows users to track bets, analyze performance, and follow profitable tipsters.

Built with Next.js 15 (App Router), TypeScript, and Prisma ORM with strong emphasis on type safety.

- It's deployed on Vercel
- Database is Neon serverless Postgres with Prisma ORM
- Authentication is Firebase Auth with session cookies
- File storage is Google Cloud Storage for profile pictures and assets
- Caching is Redis (Upstash) for user data and performance optimization
- Payment processing is Stripe for subscriptions and billing
- Cloud functions are Firebase Functions for background processing
- Monitoring is Sentry for error tracking
- External tipster data comes from Supabase integration